features: 🩷【Storage Cabinet with Sliding Doors 】This storage cabinet is wood & acrylic, visible, beautiful. Sliding doors don't require additional space for opening and closing, super easy to get things you need, as they slide horizontally along a track. This is particularly advantageous in homes with limited space. It can enhance the overall aesthetic appeal of your entryway, particularly to maximum light filtration, creating an airy and bright atmosphere. Perfect for hallway, entryway, or any room.

💛【Storage Cabinet for Small Spaces 】Our storage accent cabinet is perfect for small spaces with its reasonable size(12.6"D x 31.4" W x 51.2"H ), you don't need a large space but have a storage cabinet can hold a hundred of items because it's sliding doors and large capacity layers. So you can maximize the storage capacity with the smallest spaces.

💜【 Beautiful Accent Cabinet 】This accent cabinet is stylish and beautiful. It has 2 arched shape acrylic doors which is special and artic. With golden brush handles and 4 elegant legs, it is an overall aesthetic accent cabinet that can decorate any room like the entryway, hallway, kitchen, or living room.

🩵【Ample Storage with Adjustable Shelves & Drawers】With 2 adjustable shelves, you can adjust the height you need, and the 3-tire 2 shelves(12.6"D x 31.5"W x 12.2"H } have a large and spacious room to place so many items. About 2 wood drawers can store personal items, with a golden brushed handle which is sturdy and easier to pull than other plastic handles. The top shelf offers a large storage and display space to show your decorations. The total capacity can hold up to 520 lbs.

💚【Wide Application】This utility storage cabinet can be used as an accent cabinet, entryway cabinet, bookcase, liquor cabinet, or pantry and sideboard buffet, perfect for your entryway, kitchen, or livingroom. Such a beautiful and versatile storage cabinet will satisfy all your needs and make the room you placed more prominent and visually appealing.

reviews.reviewText: So much more engineering in this than a lot of Ikea furniture. The pieces start out feeling flimsy but after a LOT of construction it feels sturdy and looks great. Use your own tools if you have them, they include a tiny screwdriver but this has so many screws that your hand will be dying by the time you’re done if you’re not using a more comfortable screwdriver.
